<h3>Cache Control</h3>

<% form_tag :action => "expire" do %>
  <%= submit_tag "Expire Cache", :class => "button", :style => "margin:0px;" %>
<% end %>

<p>This will delete all cached files so that they'll be regenerated on their next request.  This is useful for when new issues are published.  So that they actually get, you know, published.</p>
